2026-04-07T00:17:31.8514128Z [36;1m    # Extract hit/miss from verbose lines[0m
2026-04-07T00:17:31.8514737Z [36;1m    hm = re.findall(r'dns:(\d+)h/(\d+)m', text)[0m
